txt.en: 'Speak with me to level up your reputation with the Council of the North.'

'Greetings. Keth has decided that I should be a bestower for the \qCouncil of the North\q reputation faction, so here I am. Also, if you need a Sindarin name, um, well I can't help you, as this is just a quest, but I come up with those as well.

Anyway, enough about me, I can make you an \qAcquaintance\q of the Council of the North, if you wish.

'If this sounds agreeable to you, speak to me again!'
'Alright, soon the Council of the North will consider you an Acquaintance. Ready?'
Angmar - Council of the North I
By completing this quest, you will be considered an Acquaintance of the Council of the North.
